{
  "stem": "5388.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had the loaf of bread, and I had my two earrings and a watch.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I make an arrangement with that particular Estonian farmer who speaks Russian, that he should feed him and me, the Dutch guy and me, and he can have it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I gave it to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, now I go and had lunch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You should see a dinner, it was with potatoes, was meat, was-- oh!",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It didn't last long because what happened was we having appel, which is, you know, getting together of all the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there is this lagerfuhrer comes up, and somebody's trying to push his nephew on him as a [NON-ENGLISH], a runner, and he didn't like the choice.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And suddenly, I was standing, as I told you, in the small boy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I wasn't small, but I was still small among the people involved, so I was in the first line.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I'm in the first line of the lanes involved, and suddenly that lagerfuhrer, the commander of the camp, he winks with his finger towards my direction, to come out and to come to him.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I still don't know whether that's me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he again, this way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And finally it looks like he's-- so I show with my finger me?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I come out, and he asked me speak the Dutch?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I say yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said, OK, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the other boy did not get the job of [NON-ENGLISH], being a runner.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was thinking to myself, son of a gun.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Here I have my good food, and I get my newspapers and the news, and now I've lost it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Of course, it was a blessing in disguise.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
